							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/accountablility" rel="tag">accountablility</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/extradition-2" rel="tag">extradition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nsa" rel="tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/russia" rel="tag">Russia</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/usa" rel="tag">USA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
